Narrative: It Ends With Us by Colleen Hoover is the story of a woman’s struggle to break the cycle of abuse and rise above to create a safe life not only for herself but for her child. A tearjerker, this book is not only inspiring but also one of those books that leave an indelible mark on a reader’s heart.
Title: It Ends With Us
